moji\" /> 之類<br />\n加油 共勉之"},{"pid":"1cfb9a70ab1c375e4dbd27c13076ccadc5390725","tid":2178771,"uid":42224,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T15:41:27.000Z","msg":"我食通便梅都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有正常食菜 但都冇屎痾 完全唔知食咗嘅野去哂邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7c89d1cc84bd6130f7d6fe5972b42d58a21fa74","tid":2178771,"uid":165142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cfb9a70ab1c375e4dbd27c13076ccadc5390725","tid":2178771,"uid":42224,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T15:41:27.000Z","msg":"我食通便梅都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有正常食菜 但都冇屎痾 完全唔知食咗嘅野去哂邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T15:47:00.000Z","msg":"我食綠日堂果隻 <br />\n算係天然野 柯到死咗<br />\n個個fd食完都柯 <br />\n你可以試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家加油"},{"pid":"cc3dba71f02db6cd6bb3573fcd1e409c61f5fb51","tid":2178771,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T15:47:04.000Z","msg":"唔食菜日日痾到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n太多纖維同蛋白質好難痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd9f5e96ae305d55bdacb114dfab12dce6fc108f","tid":2178771,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T15:47:48.000Z","msg":"食oak milk+ 全麥維先keep住有得痀"},{"pid":"37c583cfa27b8b449f50a1864f41b91d1fcf8f12","tid":2178771,"uid":66248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T15:48:31.000Z","msg":"新鳥飛嗚s"},{"pid":"188c5d18f238e1ff0158a10d94ac979eaa58f321","tid":2178771,"uid":45821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T15:48:33.000Z","msg":"一個星期屙一次屎  睇到都覺得辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9baee099717b74